title: 【告知あり】マリン船長、大型アプデで美少女に磨きがかかってしまう──【ホロライブ/宝鐘マリン】
name: Houshou Marine

entries.text: No, no? Can't buy a ship, no, no?
Won't you sell us your treasure?
Now, it's the captain of the Houshou Pirates...
I caught a bit of a cold.
Of all people, Marine made a mistake.
I meant to show this later...
I'm putting it away, so please wait.
I was planning to show it later.
I want to show you this super update.
I also have some exciting announcements.
And recent events, since I feel like I haven't talked about what's been happening lately.
I sound super nasal, don't I? I'm really sorry.
My voice hasn't changed, it's just a stuffy nose.
I've said the same thing three times now.
I want to show you my cute face.
Honestly, my nose... if I look down...
It starts dripping, so I want to blow it.
But I can't exactly blow it right now...
And I can't sniff it back up either.
Oh right, do you guys know...
I lost a bit there, gotta be careful.
But, you guys, from a guy's perspective...
But actually, from a girl's perspective...
...is cute and makes us want to give chocolate.
I'm going to blow my nose, so please wait a moment.
I want to update the face and chat with a cute face.
I feel like, "Let's just update already!" Come on, hurry up.
"Is that okay for an old guy to do?"
Ah, he wants them so bad! He's practically saying "I want to eat truffles!"
Marine thinks it'd be nice if he got some.
If he's a boss at work...
Maybe we should give some out?
But conversely, at a company, you *have* to give them out.
If we have to think about that...
It's actually helpful to know what he wants.
I'll become Marine and *then* give you chocolate.
It's obviously better if I'm cuter.
So I'll get cuter and give you chocolate.
Do Holomembers give chocolates to each other?
I don't think so? Not really.
The diligent girls do when it's close to Valentine's.
Koyori and Noel-chan are the diligent types.
By the way, Marine is not diligent with events at all.
So I'll maintain my cynicism and say...
Can I really be this cute?
Noel-chan doesn't cry at times like this.
She's the type to get exasperated.
I'll give you a cool smile.
Ah, my facial muscles have become super rich!
I'm going to get taken to Fuji Safari Park!
Oh no, what should I do?!
They'll haul me off to Fuji Safari Park!
No! The male lions will target me!
Marine is too cute, it's scary!
I can make really subtle faces now.
I can do subtle faces, so I'll do one now.
I can even stick out my tongue.
It's a "Is the kiss coming yet?" face.
No matter how you look at it.
Also the mouth goes like this...
A normal smile looks like this, but...
I'm trying my best to do it.
What do I want to show you, you guys?
What does cute Marine want to do...
Chocolate melting all sticky on my chest.
Next, I want you to see this.
My nose is dripping because I looked down.
Wait, you can't see this one.
So I want you to take my chocolate—wait, can I blow my nose? Just a sec.
I have a cold, so there might be some cold germs or snot or sneezes on it...
But hey, they say "in sickness and in health," right?
So when Captain has a cold...
I want you to catch a cold too.
I want you to throw away your umbrella.
I want you to eat my snot too.
You said you wanted to use Captain Marine's snot as skin lotion!
There's no other woman like this!
If you fall for a normal anime character...
Marine is with you through it all.
"If you look closely, did you cut your hair?"
Even though it changed this much...
In that sense, yes, it was fixed.
My neck is tired from tilting, can I go back to normal?
So, Pekora gave me one for Christmas...
So I bought the same one.
I'm not crying from being busy or anything.
Tears, snot, saliva, everything dries up completely.
Allergy meds are like powerful drugs.
Really, I get all dried out.
I don't sweat much originally anyway...
All the moisture in my body flies away.
You wanted to be looked at...
I'm not giving you any chocolate.
Since you seemed to have complaints...
I should tell you my schedule for later before I forget.
Actually, I have a lot to tell you.
Marine has a big job to do.
There's work for the Kumarin mascot.
I'm going to deliver some cuteness!
They apparently want to talk to Marine-tan too.
Marine-tan will talk, then send out Kumarin.
I'm going to push my cuteness on them.
It's a call-in, so it'll be brief.
Did I say such a thing?
Recording for other members' anniversary lives...
I decided to write them all.
Since I said I'd write them all...
I said, "I can do it! I want to do it!"
I was like, "Are they really doubting me this much?"
Well, it's my first time writing *all* of them.
I said, "I'll do it myself! I can do it!"
I'm working hard on it right now.
Ah, no, 4 boxes. I already sent one.
I finished sending one, so 3 remain.
Actually, I finished 2 boxes. One is sent.
I'm preparing to send the second one.
And I'm starting on the third one now.
So I'll finish with time to spare.
You can make channels in a server, right?
If it exceeds 500, you can't make new channels.
So we had to make a new server.
It's not like we had the server since the beginning.
We gradually switched to using a server.
At first, I managed work via DMs with my manager.
Since the second manager was in the server...
It was before the Gen 3 Live?
Before I knew it, we passed 500 and needed a new server.
I thought, "Wow, we've done so much."
We manage all those various things on the server.
And for Shorts, I made a separate server for video production.
So if you count those in detail, there are even more.
"Please let me do a dental checkup."
Ah, I laughed. I didn't want to laugh.
I went to the dentist recently and had none.
They check for cavities every time.
I can do that Kasuga face impression.
Thinking about all the work I've done...
Being able to do face impressions...
Honestly, don't you think that's rich?
In JP, I think only Fubu-chan...
I can only use it with my default outfit...
And I can't use it in collabs.
If I host, I can use it.
I'm waiting eagerly for further updates.
Before the Gen 3 Live, I caught a cold.
If I said "Cold before a Live"...
Afterward, I reported, "Actually, I had a cold but it's gone."
I started catching a cold a bit ago.
But if I say I have a cold *now*...
"You had one just the other day, are you stupid?"
I thought you might think that.
I couldn't say "I have a cold."
I decided I'd definitely do it.
But if I stream, it's obviously a cold.
This is obviously a cold voice.
I'll get exposed as having a cold.
So I thought I'd just honestly admit I caught one.
That saying is weird, isn't it?
So actually, I had a cold...
...in a situation where I couldn't say anything.
My cover song with Salome-san went up.
Did you guys listen to it?
It was a "Let's talk scam" where we never did.
Can I blow my nose once? Sorry.
While saying that, we couldn't talk.
But getting to do a cover...
Doing such a gorgeous cover together...
But it makes a gross sound...
It became my first song collab.
This is a collection of stories from a bit ago...
I met quite a few Holomembers.
I think someone mentioned this, but...
I went to dinner with Watame, Ui, and Koyori.
...various issues came up so we couldn't do it.
We went to eat once, maybe?
"Take care"... I looked like I wanted to be taken care of.
While Marine was swishing the meat (shabu-shabu)...
We were fighting over the work.
Ah, I've met Sui-chan a few times too.
Often. Not really for dinner, though.
I met Korone for the first time in a while.
"Why are you so glossy and cute?"
I asked, and my manager also...
During her break, she lived a regular life...
So she might have become glossy because of that.
But since she's doing endurance streams again...
Curing a cold just to catch another.
Caught a cold, throat went bad.
So I started taking stream slots for Terraria...
The steroid inhaler I got before...
My health is constantly bad, what should I do?
"Steroids make it easier to catch colds."
I thought of it like ointment for the throat.
There are steroid ointments for the body, right?
I honestly don't know where I'm catching these colds.
But I am going out a lot.
I go to lessons a lot.
On days when I didn't have...
I'd draw like crazy, write messages...
There was that. The Motomachi Grill tasting event.
So it might not come across.
I eat a lot of fried food.
I want to go to that.
I want to go in summer.
But Senchou has a cat allergy.
If I go to Flare's house...
My sneezing might not stop due to the allergy.
Apparently she has a machine at home.
People who are super good at rhythm games...
When you watch them, you go "Ooh!", right?
Eyes itch, nose runs, sneezing won't stop.
No, Marine can't do them at all.
But way back in the early days...
We played rhythm games at the arcade.
We got massages and went to karaoke together.
"You go to karaoke?" You might think.
You might feel that way, but...
It's like she gave it to me.
Mari didn't have a way to purchase it.
So she bought it by proxy.
She searched for a long time.
"The old one passed the directional setting, but this time..."
Moved away like "Humph", the voice would get...
At voice training, recently, ReGLOSS comes around Senchou's time slot.
I always think "I want to say hi"...
But it's usually overlapping with Senchou leaving.
They won't come unless I wait.
But Senchou has the next appointment, so I have to go.
So on the way out, occasionally...
I see a glimpse of them coming from afar.
The voice trainer introduced by Hololive Management...
Recordings where we interacted in the past...
I don't have any images for the announcement yet.
So I want to unveil it gradually...
I mentioned I was drawing pictures.
I said I was drawing pictures for goods.
Including the ones I consulted about there...
After going through various offline lives...
Wait, snot is getting caught in my throat.
I thought I want to see you wearing it.
"Even though the Birthday goods just arrived?"
I'm sorry it's one thing after another.
But for this one, no matter what...
Geared towards playing card games, I think.
I thought of goods like that.
I absolutely, absolutely want you to get this one.
It includes designs I thought of together with you guys too.
Yes, please look forward to it.
I was invited to call in.
I have plans to go, but...
So I thought I'd read Superchats.
Phlegm gets stuck and it goes *rattle rattle*.
Why is my health so bad, Senchou?
No good. My immune system is finished. Seriously.
No, with the Superchats, it's different. Look...
I recorded my impressions after getting back.
I said "I'll read Superchats next time" and ended it without reading.
So I intend to read those.
This time, even if I go to the bad parts...
I'll definitely forget if I push it back too far.
In the past, when I was young, for a diet...
When I focused on vegetables, my health was terrible.
Someone, make Marine eat a balanced meal.
But I want to eat fried food in the end.
Even if you make me a balanced meal...
"Ehh, I want to eat fried food today~"
"People eating tons of McD's with clear skin..."
Surely eating vegetables makes skin clearer.
Eh, Senchou doesn't get it from McD's.
If I eat Kalbi at Yakiniku...
Two slices and I get heartburn.
Even though it changed this much, you don't know?
Return confirmed, I can eat it.
Eh, this one? This one, right?
This definitely has an overseas vibe expression.
I can make lots of faces.
Well, I was playing Terraria for a long time.
"My health is bad, so let's sleep."
Senchou sleeps with her arms raised.
And because of this, my shoulders hurt.
Even at dance, "Rotate your neck like this."
Originally, Senchou wasn't the type to sleep with arms up.
"Autonomic nerves" always comes up, doesn't it?
But honestly, I think my autonomic nerves *are* messed up.
Can I blow my nose a sec?
I think my autonomic nerves are probably messed up.
The hand holding the pen would lose strength.
Also when waking up, I can't make a fist.
I looked that up back then.
It said that happens when autonomic nerves are bad.
I'm always told it's autonomic nerves.
What are they? How do you fix them?
Anyway, from the moment I wake up...
My first words aren't "Good morning," but immediately upon waking...
"Ah, wait, ouch, ah, tired..." I say that.
When you get old, the topic becomes health.
It really was true that topics become just that.
Not that, but... a long time ago, Washagana TV...
I opened Washagana TV's live stream...
"The old men are talking about hospitals forever."
Marine is starting to become that.
"This auntie is talking about hospitals again."
"This auntie is talking about bad health again."
...who only talks about health. Be careful.
Talking only about bad health and hospitals.
Even though I want to be adored.
This chocolate stuck in her cleavage...
Ah, I can make a super lewd face.
Who cares about that other stuff.
I can make a lewd face.
Watch, I'm doing a lewd face.
My cheeks really puff out, see?
Whether it's restricted to 18+ or not.
Are you kissing the screen right now?
Maybe I shouldn't say this after kissing but...
I have a cold right now...
"Do you take care of your breath?"
You're probably just kissing your smartphone screen!
It's your smartphone screen that smells!
Marine really hasn't read Superchats in a while.
So I want to read Superchats.
For those who want to Superchat...
Or those who want to stare at Marine...
Please watch in a new window.
I need to write "Superchat Reading Time".
I gotta reply to the Gen 3 chat.
Umm, which one are we watching?
Let's watch, since it won't be viewable soon.
Playing with the chocolate's good spots.
You want this done to you, right?
Man, I'm happy I got cuter.
Ah, right, that hasn't been decided yet~.
Since I have a new face...
I wanted to sing songs and stuff.
My nose is just too stuffed...
I'm probably not in a state to sing.
I had a cold recently too...
If they think "She rescheduled for a cold recently and has a cold *again*?"
So I'm desperately trying to cure it.
I'm seriously trying hard right now.
I absolutely have to fix it by the recording.
"This old hag, how many times will she catch a cold?"
If it were lines, I could manage.
If it's lines, I can clear my nose a bit...
And push through with nose drops.
But for singing, there's nothing I can do.
So I have to cure it out of stubbornness.
Why do I get sick so much?
Hey, Senchou wants to do a singing stream too.
Ah, I finally finished scrolling back.
If there's detailed content, I'll read it.
I'll blow my nose once, excuse me.
"Old fan appeal." Nice, old fan appeal.
Even if you thought that then...
Now, if you say "I knew since Eiyashou"...
Even if you're new now, in a few years you'll be old-school.
But usually the oldest fans are...
"Going to find a place to cohabit."
Muting to blow my nose is getting...
What do you think, you guys?
If I don't mute, it's unpleasant, right?
It's SC reading, maybe it's fine?
Well, if there are people who dislike it, I'll stop.
"Were the lyrics displayed on stage handwritten by you?"
Where if you put your hand close...
Soaked by that and she had to rewrite it. I told that story.
Flare-chan gave it to the staff...
She thought you might think she did it.
I used a whole box of tissues just today.
I worry if people will get excited.
I go on stage with a bit of anxiety.
Though with Gen 3, it's just 4 of us...
So usually everyone has their oshi there.
Like Ui's Live, will it be okay?
I've collabed with Ui many times.
Look forward to what I do with Ui.
Usually there are so many hard ones.
"An indie doing a Birthday Live at K-Arena is insane."
Shigure Ui is seriously the hegemony.
I want to be her too! I want to be Shigure Ui!
Senchou drinks water with a straw...
When I drink with a straw...
A mountain of tissues is spreading.
It was a tumbler in the gift exchange.
Holds over 800ml, so I fill it up.
Once they're in a pile, I'll throw them.
I can't throw them one by one.
Right? Senchou can't throw away tissues?
The moment I desperately need a tissue...
I've had that experience many times in life.
Scared of running out of tissues.
"Put a trash can at your feet."
"Just throw it away one by one."
It's cute, so I'm liking them bit by bit.
Also sorry my throat is gurgling.
When I struggle to breathe, my throat gurgles.
Even if I blow and blow...
Even if I blow... nose is just...
I'll stuff tissues in my nose.
"Doesn't it hurt?" It hurts like hell.
"If we can't send presents, buy it yourself with Superchats." Thank you.
It's okay, I'll buy it myself.
The goods coming out for 4 Million subs...
I want you to buy *that* instead.
I want you to buy that.
I want to see it with my own eyes.
If I make Kyuuichi spend money on SCs...
You might not be able to buy the goods.
So I want you to get *that*.
Sorry, tried not to sniff, but I sniffed.
I used it in a different place.
So I tried to make use of it.
"Will I not be able to buy the goods?" If you think that...
Stop sending SCs and buy the goods instead.
"I'll convince myself it was for me."
I have work, can I make it?
"Eat well and sleep well is key."
But when my throat is wrecked...
And the messages reach you guys.
Writing while thinking "I'm talking to Kyuuichi".
Feels like I'm interacting, it's nice.
I can feel connected to Kyuuichi.
Are mixed with Virus Handwritten Cards.
"If Marine infiltrated an Ichimi offline meet."
"Ichimi meetups are really like this," everyone said.
Actually, the version I thought of was lewder.
I thought of... well, the intro...
I only thought of the lewd part ahead.
To make it for the general public...
That gave off a "this will get lewd" vibe...
So I scraped off all those elements...
Really, it was supposed to be...
Thinking about various things, it all vanished.
I'll blow my nose a bit.
"Ah-un" sounds are getting in a lot.
I thought it was super audible.
This mic picks up sound well.

By the time we get to SC reading...
The guys saying "Grass" or "Smells like Gyouza"...
Those Smartphone Gyouza Bastards are gone.
"I had ramen today, do I smell?"
My nose is stuffed, I can't tell.
Why was no tissue coming out?
Before I knew it, I pulled it out.
Before I knew it, I pulled it.
"This SC is the initial cost for living with Marine."
"Marine said she wanted to live together."
Ah, might as well make a lewd face.
Kyuuichi, crazy, this is too erotic.

Isn't it erotic? This is crazy.
"Face when there are about 4 pages left."
I'll do the "4 pages left" face.
"Can you peel it off for Captain Marine?"
What to do for the middle part.
What to do for the middle part.
"Face when a technique battle starts in front of you."
Then "Face when seeing a weakling Ichimi."
Or is the opposing Ichimi too good? Which? That face.
Conversely, face when it's too long.
"Who are you talking to? Are Ichimi watching too?"
We're watching with the waiting Ichimi.
Ichimi are preparing to watch the technique battle.
Probably if I don't open my mouth...
Seems Seiso if I don't speak.
Thank you so much for so many.
Sorry I just read names quickly.
I'm really happy I could meet you guys.
I want to meet again, and next time...
Right, seeing you guys, I thought...
When the venue opens and you guys start taking seats, we're watching like this.
"Ah, that one's an Elfriend! Look, they have Flare-chan's plushie!"
"That one is Ichimi, right? Wearing striped clothes."
So I thought, Ichimi seriously wear stripes, so "That's definitely Ichimi."
So I don't want to give up the stripes.
"Not stripes, we want black shirts for daily use."
We can make a "That's a Marine fan" face.
I can make that face and...
I can make that face and be happy.
I made you wear looks that identify you as Ichimi.
To the level of worrying about cutting them...
I definitely want you to buy *that*.
I want to see in the future.
End of Feb, 4 Million Celebration Stream.
"She's doing this?" Look forward to it.
"Come to think of it, she mentioned that," things like that will appear.
I think I'll end it for now.
On a Gen 3 member's channel, sometime after 19:00.
